0:00:00.000,0:00:02.940
Mangwanani akanaka chechi!

0:00:02.940,0:00:06.120
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:00:06.120,0:00:17.200
Zita rangu ndi Ochomma Uche. Ini ndinobva ku Imo State, Nigeria.

0:00:17.200,0:00:20.360
Uchapupu hwangu hune zvikamu zviviri

0:00:20.360,0:00:26.240
Chikamu chekutanga ndechekureurura.

0:00:26.240,0:00:42.840
Ndaive nhengo yechechi, neboka revanhu vainenedzera munhu wa Mwari, vaiparidza zvinopikisana naye,

0:00:42.840,0:00:54.020
vaimudana nemazita akaipa kwete chete mugungano redu asiwo kune mamwe machechi.

0:00:54.020,0:01:01.240
Ndakanga ndiri nhengo yehutungamiri hukuru mu Nigeria.

0:01:01.240,0:01:03.560
Taive nezita ratakamupa.

0:01:03.560,0:01:07.660
Zvinosuruvarisa chaizvo kutaura izvi asi ini ndino zvitaura kuti kubwinya kwa Mwari kuonekwe.

0:01:07.660,0:01:10.660
Vaiwanzomuti "tuberculosis".

0:01:10.660,0:01:15.960
Kana waive nhengo yechechi iyoyo uye iwe uri pano zvino - danidzira "Hareruya!".

0:01:15.960,0:01:20.760
Ndinoziva kuti vamwe vavo vari pano.

0:01:20.760,0:01:23.920
Rumbidzai Mwari!

0:01:23.920,0:01:33.440
Ndaimbova mufundisi uye gare gare nhengo yechechi iyi, yandakuudzai nezvayo.

0:01:33.440,0:01:41.380
Takafamba tichishora munhu wa Mwari, tichitaura zvakaipa pamusoro pake, tichimudana mazita emarudzi ose,

0:01:41.380,0:01:45.260
tichimuti "satani" pachake.

0:01:45.260,0:01:57.060
Apo takanga tichiita izvi, zvakaitika kwandiri kuti murume uyu wandinopikisa, wandinotonga -

0:01:57.060,0:01:59.980
Handisati ndambonzwa shoko rake.

0:01:59.980,0:02:01.900
Handina kumbo...

0:02:01.900,0:02:06.320
Handikwanise kuyeuka chero shoko rake raizove rinotsamwisa.

0:02:06.320,0:02:10.780
Saka ndakasarudza kuti, "Kwete. Ndichatarisa kumagwaro."

0:02:10.780,0:02:17.320
Mweya wangu wakandiudza kuti ndiende kuna Mabasa aVapositori 17:11.

0:02:17.320,0:02:24.800
Chinoita kuti munhu kuti arumbinzwe kukwanisa kwake kuteerera izwi ne kurifananidza nemagwaro,

0:02:24.800,0:02:27.380
kunze kwe zvishamiso.

0:02:27.380,0:02:31.380
Nokuti kushure kwechishamiso chipi zvacho panofanira kuva ne Shoko.

0:02:31.380,0:02:39.300
Saka, izvi zvakandiita kuti ndione Emmanuel TV kuti ndingonzwa munhu wa Mwari.

0:02:39.300,0:02:50.800
Apo ndakatanga kuterera ku Emmanuel TV, mhuri yangu yakanditsamwira

0:02:50.800,0:02:55.520
nokuti waisagona kutarisa Emmanuel TV mumba mangu.

0:02:55.520,0:03:01.780
Kunyange iko zvino, vamwe vangu vari pasi pangu vafundisi, vavhangeri -

0:03:01.780,0:03:08.260
pakarepo pandino batidza Emmanuel TV, vose vanobva.

0:03:08.260,0:03:10.000
Rumbidzai Mwari!

0:03:10.000,0:03:18.380
Ndine urombo, changamire, musati maenda mberi - mataura kuti maive mufundisi muushumiri ihwohwo uye maive makabatana navo

0:03:18.380,0:03:24.500
mukutaura zvinhu zvakawanda zvisina kunaka pamusoro peushumiri hwe pano - Pa SCOAN.

0:03:24.500,0:03:31.140
Munogona kungotsanangura zvishoma shoma; somuenzaniso mhando yeminyengetero yamakanga muchipa panguva iyoyo

0:03:31.140,0:03:35.740
ne zvinhu zvamaitaura panguva iyoyo?

0:03:35.740,0:03:45.680
Zvakanaka, iwe unogona kufungidzira zvaungataura pamusoro pomurume uyu, ane mazwi ausina kumbonzwa.

0:03:45.680,0:03:54.660
Nokuti aiva maonero emukuru wedu GO, ndiyo waiva mirairo waitarisirwa isu tika vimba naye.

0:03:54.660,0:04:00.440
Saka, takamutora <T.B. Joshua> semunhu anopesana na Kristu pachake - zimukadzimu ra satani,

0:04:00.440,0:04:08.360
uyo aive achiita zvishamiso nemasimba akanga asiri a Mwari.

0:04:08.360,0:04:11.580
Ndiri kutaura nezve mu Porofita T.B. Joshua - hongu.

0:04:11.580,0:04:19.080
Ndakanzwa kuti ndaifanira kunzwa kubva kumurume uyu, kunzwa mashoko ake, kutsvagurudza mumagwaro, kuziva kana zvaari kutaura

0:04:19.080,0:04:20.840
zvichienderana nemagwaro.

0:04:20.840,0:04:24.000
Ndakatanga kuona Emmanuel TV.

0:04:24.000,0:04:36.280
Nekushamisa kwangu kukuru, dzidziso dzake dzose, mazwi ose aaidzidzisa, ne kunzwisisika kwawo, ose aive

0:04:36.280,0:04:38.860
achienderana nemagwaro.

0:04:38.860,0:04:47.760
Reururo ya Baba Ochoma Uche / Uchapupu hwe Dzikinuro

0:04:47.760,0:04:50.040
Zvinosvika ...

0:04:50.040,0:04:56.240
Dzidziso yake yakanyatsojeka.

0:04:56.240,0:05:01.980
Ndakatanga kuona mu Porofita nenzira yakasiyana.

0:05:01.980,0:05:07.920
Ndakatanga kunzwa kuti zvichida ndaive ndichipa mhosva munhu asina mhosva.

0:05:07.920,0:05:10.200
Ndakanga ndichi taura zvakaipa pamusoro pomunhu asina mhosva.

0:05:10.200,0:05:15.820
Pandega ndakawira muimba yangu yekurara ndikakumbira kuna Mwari ndichiti, "Mwari, ndiregererei".

0:05:15.820,0:05:18.460
Ndinorangarira zuva iroro.

0:05:18.460,0:05:22.440
Ndakareurura, ndakati, "Mwari, ndiregererei".

0:05:22.440,0:05:29.760
Kufarira kwangu kwakawedzera kusvika pakuti ndakasarudza kuti ndaizouya kuzoshanyira SCOAN

0:05:29.760,0:05:37.620
Iwe unogona kufungidzira; Ini ndiri nhengo yechechi kwandinoparidzira zvinopikisana ne munhu wa Mwari - mu Porofita T.B. Joshua - hongu.

0:05:37.620,0:05:41.680
Panguva imwe chete ini ndaive ndichiita "zvivi zvakavanzika".

0:05:41.680,0:05:54.980
Ndainwa, ndaiputa, ini ndichiita zve madzimai - fungidzira izvozvo ...

0:05:54.980,0:06:01.280
Kuti munhu ane zvinhu izvi muhupenyu hwake angagone kupomera munhu wa Mwari sei?

0:06:01.280,0:06:04.100
Ndakazviita.

0:06:04.100,0:06:09.140
Zvose izvi zvakaitika muupenyu hwangu kuti kubwinya kwa Mwari kuonekwe.

0:06:09.140,0:06:23.760
Chokwadi ndechekuti: kana iwe uri mu Kristu anekukosha kupi zvako, hapana chimwe chezvinhu zvandakambotaura chingaita kuti iwe umire zvakasimba

0:06:23.760,0:06:26.940
pamberi pa Mwari.

0:06:26.940,0:06:29.020
Kwete!

0:06:29.020,0:06:30.320
Ndinoziva kuti ...

0:06:30.320,0:06:42.860
Hongu, ndakanga ndiri muushumiri, ndakanga ndichidzidzisa nekuparidza asi mukati mangu ndaiziva kuti izvi zvose zvaive "pasina".

0:06:42.860,0:06:48.900
Ndakaedza kuviga zvivi zvangu munzira dzakawanda.

0:06:48.900,0:06:56.360
Ndaifamba makiromita mazana maviri, kure neguta, kuitira kuti ndiende kunozvifadza.

0:06:56.360,0:07:02.460
Ndaizoenda usiku kunzvimbo dzakasviba kuitira kuti ndipute.

0:07:02.460,0:07:10.080
Ndaizonwa muchivande munzvimbo dzausingafungiri, nokuti handidi vabereki vangu

0:07:10.080,0:07:17.620
vateedzani vangu, nhengo dzechechi yangu kuti vazive kuti ndinoita mabasa akadaro.

0:07:17.620,0:07:19.400
Ini ndiri hama yavo.

0:07:19.400,0:07:23.840
Ndakarwisana nezvinhu izvi kwenguva refu.

0:07:23.840,0:07:27.220
Ndakanyengetera, ndakatsanya ...

0:07:27.220,0:07:34.140
Ndinoyeuka kuti ndakatsanya kwemazuva manomwe kuti Ishe aifanira kubvisa kutambudzika uku kubva kwandiri.

0:07:34.140,0:07:39.380
mazuva maviri kumatatu mushure mekutsanya ndakadzokera kwazviri.

0:07:39.380,0:07:42.960
Ndaiziva kuti rakanga riri dambudziko guru.

0:07:42.960,0:07:46.520
Imi changamire mati maivanza mabasa aya.

0:07:46.520,0:07:50.500
Dzimwe nguva maifanirwa kufamba rwendo rurefu kuti munozvifadza.

0:07:50.500,0:07:59.000
Ingotsanangurai, imi pamaifamba rwendo rurefu, chii chamazviona muchiita ikoko, kunyange semufundisi.

0:07:59.000,0:08:03.580
Zvechokwadi, ndakaenda kunze kuti ndinovanza zvivi zvangu.

0:08:03.580,0:08:08.740
Ndakabuda kunze kuitira kuti pasave ne maziso aizondiona ndichiita zvitadzo izvi, kuti vanhu vekuziva vasandione

0:08:08.740,0:08:14.540
vozondiziva somunhu anoita zvinhu zvakadaro.

0:08:14.540,0:08:17.280
Ndicho chikonzero nei ndaifanira kuvanza.

0:08:17.280,0:08:21.720
Hongu, kurara nevakadzi, pfambi, kunwa ...

0:08:21.720,0:08:25.380
Ndakaita zvinhu zvakadaro, ndakazviita - hongu.

0:08:25.380,0:08:31.800
Zvakanga zvakarema pamweya wangu, nokuti ndinoziva kuti hakuna munhu anoita zvinhu zvakadaro

0:08:31.800,0:08:34.720
achagara nhaka yekudenga.

0:08:34.720,0:08:40.140
Zvakanyatsojeka kwandiri.

0:08:40.140,0:08:47.480
Ndakasarudza kushanyira Emmanuel TV mushure mekuona zvishamiso pano.

0:08:47.480,0:08:50.800
Pakutanga, handina kuve ne ha'na nekutarisa zvishamiso.

0:08:50.800,0:08:58.260
Ndakanga ndichida Shoko, nokuti takadzikinurwa ne Shoko, kuburikidza ne Shoko.

0:08:58.260,0:09:04.140
Apo ini ndakateerera ku Shoko, ndakawana kuti Shoko raive rakarurama - saka ndakave ne simba rekuuya pano.

0:09:04.140,0:09:15.200
Hama, pandakauya pano kokutanga hapana munhu akandibata - ndakangopinda svondo yemusi we Svondo.

0:09:15.200,0:09:19.040
Ndakaenda kumba.

0:09:19.040,0:09:26.420
Pandakabva pano hama, ndisina kumbobatwa nomunhu wa Mwari, ndisina kuporofitwa,

0:09:26.420,0:09:32.700
mweya we kunwa, kusvuta nekufambidzana ne madzimai wakandisiya zviro kwazvo.

0:09:32.700,0:09:39.640
Reururo ya Baba Ochoma Uche / Uchapupu hwe Dzikinuro

0:09:39.640,0:09:51.480
Chakava chiratidzo chaicho kwandiri kuti muna Mwari munzvimbo ino.

0:09:51.480,0:09:52.800
Emanueri!

0:09:52.800,0:09:54.860
[Mwari anesu.]

0:09:54.860,0:10:02.040
Hama, izvi ndizvo zvinhu zvataita pamusoro pa T.B. Joshua.

0:10:02.040,0:10:04.500
Ndiri kunamata kuti anondikanganwira.

0:10:04.500,0:10:06.820
Ndinoreurura pachena pa ruzhinji.

0:10:06.820,0:10:08.860
Ndinoziva kuti ari kunzwa izwi rangu.

0:10:08.860,0:10:15.840
Regai vandiregerere pane zvandakaita pamusoro pavo.

0:10:15.840,0:10:17.900
Ndave kuuya kune zvakaitika pano zuro.

0:10:17.900,0:10:24.260
Nezuro, apo munhu wa Mwari aiparidza, ndakanga ndichinzwa zvakaipa zvakanyanya mukati mangu.

0:10:24.260,0:10:29.160
Zvaiita sekunge ndaive ndigere pazviuru zvezvipeneti

0:10:29.160,0:10:34.340
Musana wangu, chiuno changu, dumbu rangu zvaipisa.

0:10:34.340,0:10:38.760
Ndainzwa kupisa mukati - kusagadzikana kwakanyanya.

0:10:38.760,0:10:48.060
Ndakanga ndichirwadziwa zvakanyanya zvokuti ndaifunga kuti kufa kwaizova nani kwandiri kupfuura kugara nemarwadzo akadaro mumuviri wangu.

0:10:48.060,0:10:53.320
Asi apo izvi zvaive zvichifamba nomuviri wangu, ndakarangarira mazwi ake,

0:10:53.320,0:10:58.540
"Zvinhu zvose izvi zvakauya kuzobvisa mufaro wako. Zvirambe!"

0:10:58.540,0:11:03.800
Ini ndakati, "Kwete, hazvizobvisi mufaro wangu. Kana iwe wakafa iwe haungatore hupenyu hwangu".

0:11:03.800,0:11:05.300
Ndakaramba.

0:11:05.300,0:11:12.100
Chinhu ichi chakakwira uye chakakwirira kusvikira maziso angu asisaone.

0:11:12.100,0:11:15.560
Ndaifunga kuti ndaizowira pasi.

0:11:15.560,0:11:18.540
Zvandinoziva ndezvekuti, zvandanzwa munzeve dzangu ...

0:11:18.540,0:11:27.820
"Iri ndiro dutu rinotanga kudzikama kuchizotevera".

0:11:27.820,0:11:30.260
Kubva panguva iyoyo kurwadziwa kwakatanga kudzikira.

0:11:30.260,0:11:33.940
Ndakanzwa munhu wa Mwari achiti, "Mukurwadziwa kwako - famba!"

0:11:33.940,0:11:37.080
Ndizvo zvandakayeuka iye achitaura.

0:11:37.080,0:11:40.500
Ndakasimuka ndokutanga kufambisa mitezo yangu

0:11:40.500,0:11:45.820
Kukubwinya kwa Mwari - kurwadziwa kwakatanga kudzikira kudzikira, kudzikira.

0:11:45.820,0:11:51.100
Kusvika pa mangwanani ano, hama ndakagadzikana, ndakasimba, kugwinya.

0:11:51.100,0:11:54.040
Hapasisina marwadzo zvakare mumuviri wangu.

0:11:54.040,0:11:58.340
Ameni. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:11:58.340,0:12:03.120
Mukoma vari kugoverana nesu uchapupu hwezvakaitika ipapo ipapo zuro panguva yemunyengetero we ruzhinji

0:12:03.120,0:12:05.500
pamusoro pekurwadziwa kwakanyanya kwavaive nako.

0:12:05.500,0:12:11.960
Tinoda kunzwa kubva kwamuri zvakare mukoma; kubva zvamakatanga kutsika tsoka dzenyu mu SCOAN, imi munoreva kuti

0:12:11.960,0:12:18.820
makarega zvose zvese zvekusvuta, kunwa, zvemadzimai, izvozvo zvose zvakaguma munguva iyoyo

0:12:18.820,0:12:21.000
imi pa makatsika tsoka dzenyu muno?

0:12:21.000,0:12:22.840
Ndizvozvo.

0:12:22.840,0:12:24.840
Zvakamira, havi yacho, munoziva ...

0:12:24.840,0:12:26.520
Chero chipi nechipi chaunotanga kuita chinotanga kubva pa havi.

0:12:26.520,0:12:28.520
Zvakafanana nenyota.

0:12:28.520,0:12:32.940
Kana mukana iwowo wavemo mauri, iwe unozozvitanga.

0:12:32.940,0:12:38.940
Asi kana mukana iwowo, havi isipo, haugoni kuita chiito.

0:12:38.940,0:12:49.060
Havi, mweya wekunwa, zve madzimai, kusvuta - zvose zvakandisiya.

0:12:49.060,0:12:49.780
Rumbidzai Mwari!

0:12:49.780,0:12:54.600
Ngatiise maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu kamwe zvakare.

0:12:54.600,0:12:58.640
Tinotenda Mwari kuti mukoma wedu ari pano pakati pedu kuti agoverane nesu uchapupu uhwu.

0:12:58.640,0:13:04.980
Tinotenda kune zvidzidzo zvinokosha zvatadzidza kubva pane zvavataura pano.

0:13:04.980,0:13:13.960
Nderipi zano ramungape kune vatariri vedu pasi rose; kunyanya avo vakamboita

0:13:13.960,0:13:19.200
zvinhu zvakadaro munguva yakapfuura, kusanganisira mabasa ekunyomba muranda wa Mwari,

0:13:19.200,0:13:20.420
vakadai semu Porofita T.B. Joshua?

0:13:20.420,0:13:24.820
Imi mungavayambira sei zvichibva kune zvamakasangana nazvo mu upenyu hwenyu?

0:13:24.820,0:13:34.580
Zano rangu kwamuri nderiri: musabvumira maonero evanhu vakakupoteredza

0:13:34.580,0:13:40.660
kuti vakudzivise kuziva chokwadi iwe pachako.

0:13:40.660,0:13:51.780
Usabvumira mafungiro eruzhinji kuti akusvitse pakushamwaridzana ne veruzhinji

0:13:51.780,0:13:56.440
Usati watonga munhu, munzwe.

0:13:56.440,0:14:07.000
Usati wazvioona uchigumbura mumwe munhu, tora nguva yekuwana chokwadi pamusoro pomunhu wacho.

0:14:07.000,0:14:14.100
Zvingazove ne basa reyi kuti uuraye munhu gare gare wozoona kuti murume uyu akanga asina mhosva?

0:14:14.100,0:14:16.620
Iwe unozonzwa sei?

0:14:16.620,0:14:26.420
Unozonzwa sei kana ukabaya munhu ne bakatwa uchifunga kuti akakuvadza kana kuuraya munin'ina wako,

0:14:26.420,0:14:29.140
wozoziva kuti murume wacho akanga asina mhosva?

0:14:29.140,0:14:31.760
Iwe unozonzwa sei?

0:14:31.760,0:14:32.940
Ndizvo zvandakanzwa.

0:14:32.940,0:14:35.640
Handingadi kuti mumwe munhu anzwe saizvozvo.

0:14:35.640,0:14:41.340
Saka hama, zano rangu nderokuti tsvaga chokwadi iwe pachako

0:14:41.340,0:14:45.480
uye Mwari achapupurira munhu wa Mwari.

0:14:45.480,0:14:46.640
Rumbidzai Mwari.

0:14:46.640,0:14:51.200
Ameni. Ngatiise maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu.

0:14:51.200,0:14:56.940
Tirikuona sezvataurwa nehama yedu, murume uyo waakatanga kushora, kutaura zvinopokana, akashandisa marudzi ese

0:14:56.940,0:15:03.080
mashoko asina kunaka, akapedzisira ari munhu mumwe chete uyo Mwari akashandisa kumununura

0:15:03.080,0:15:07.780
kubva mumweya we kufambidzana ne mamwe madzima, doro, ne kusvuta.

0:15:07.780,0:15:09.340
Tinopa mbiri kuna Mwari kuti ari pano ikozvino.

0:15:09.340,0:15:15.080
Zano rekupedzisira mukoma - imi makati semufundisi makanga muchiita zvinhu izvi

0:15:15.080,0:15:19.560
Chii chaunoda kurayira vanhu avo vachiri kurwisana nematambudziko akadaro ehavi yakapinda muropa,

0:15:19.560,0:15:23.380
somumwe munhu akapfuura nemazviri akakunda kuburikidza ne dzikinuro

0:15:23.380,0:15:25.360
iyo makagamuchira nokutsika tsoka dzenyu muno?

0:15:25.360,0:15:27.620
Ndeapi mazano enyu kune vanhu vakadaro?

0:15:27.620,0:15:34.160
Zano rangu nderokuti: Ndakaedza ne simba rangu rose uye ndakakundikana.

0:15:34.160,0:15:40.660
Ndakapfuura nepakati pe dzikinuro dzakawanda; dzisina kubatsira.

0:15:40.660,0:15:45.940
Dambudziko nechivi chipi zvacho kana havi ye muropa rinobva kumweya.

0:15:45.940,0:15:53.000
Zvatinoda ndezvekupindira kwa Mwari munyaya iyi.

0:15:53.000,0:16:07.240
Uye nzvimbo yandakawana, apo munhu anogona kudzikunurwa zvechokwadi ndiyo SCOAN.

0:16:07.240,0:16:14.700
Kana iwe usingakwanisi kuwana dzikinuro kune imwe nzvimbo, regai nzvimbo ino ive yekupedzisira kwauri.

0:16:14.700,0:16:18.320
Ameni. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu.

0:16:18.320,0:16:19.920
Yeuka, tanzwa zvakataurwa nehama yedu.

0:16:19.920,0:16:23.060
Akati iye akanga akangotsika tsoka dzake muno.

